S.FORM: == kakiliman == Ke-s-mu "A-la-pow a kamu الخرطوم‎ al-Kharṭūm, kamu nipabelin Ke-s-mu" nu Su-tan kung-hee-kow a angangan. makayzaay U-kan-taay a Ni-low-he atu makayzaan I-su-pi-yaay a Cin-ni-low-he itini a makakutay, pasayamis belud pasay Ay-ci atu mulaliw micumud tu Ti-cong-hey. "Ke-s-mu" cacay ku kamu u imi zu a cihek. Ke-s-mu a kitizaan iza ku100 emang ku muenengay nu tademaw, micapi tu saamisan nu Ke-s-mu atu En-tu-man a nisakaput nu tabakiay a tukay u tademaw hakay macaliway tu 400 a emang. likisi 歷史 Ke-s-mu i 1821 a mihcaan u Ay-ci atu Mu-han-mu-te.A-li-pow-sya patizeng tu tukay, mala nu Ay-ci a hitay a katukuhan. nika zikuz balaki pasu tubang patahkal kitizaan sapisiwbaynu angangan. 1884 a mihca 3 a bulad 13 a dimiad, paicelang tu Mu-han-mu-te.Ay-ha-man-te.Ma-he-ti sakaput a hitay mitaliyuk tu nu Ing-kow sakakaay nu mikeliday ci Ca-li.cyaw-ce.ke-ten mikelid mipupu tu hitay, zikuz sakay tiniay a tukay nu Ing-Ay pulung nu hitay sebek amipatay. 1885 a mihca 1 a bulad 26 a ddimiad, mapelpelay a Ke-s-mu mangayaw. zikuz I 1898 a mihca 9 a bulad 2 adimiad, ci He-pow-te.Ci-ci-le mikelid tu Ing a hitay mademe t uku misebengay nu Ma-he-ti-pay a hitay. 1885年1月26日, . 1899 a mihcaan, Ke-s-mu mala nu Ing-Ay-Su-tan angangan nu tukay. i 1956 a mihcaan sateked mala nu Su-tan zikuz mala uyni angangan nu kanatal. 1899年, . hekal地理 Ke-s-mu tini i Su-tannu macelcelay nu tademaw a kakitizaan nu teban, mahamin itini a kanatal nu Walian saamisan angangan, pey-wi15 katukuh 16 tu, tung-cin 31 katukuh 32 tu. Ke-s-mu a dimiad u akuti'ay a alikelikenan, pitu a bulad atu walu a bulad taneng mahapinang maazih ku kasinanum. Ke-s-mu palalecad paymihcaan kasinanum macaliway ku 155 haw-mi. tini I mihcaan palalecad tu bali nu akuti', Ke-s-mu u sataledesay nu tabakiay a tukay. kalaludan akuti' hakay a macaliway ku 53˚C "127˚F". mihcaan palalecad satalakaway akuti' nu lahud 37.1˚C "99˚F". namahiza nayay ku cacanan palalecad tu nu buladay a akuti' isasa tu 30˚C "86˚F". uyni caay henay kaazih zumaay angangan akuti' ku likelikenan demiad nu tukay Li-ya-te, Pa-ke-ta-atu Bung-hwang a tukay mahiniay. u akuti' i labii mahapinang maselep ku akuti', Ke-s-mu palalecad saisasaay a lahud a didi' ku akuti'. Ke-s-mu iza ku Su-tan satabakiay a pahikukia. nu Su-tanay a pibahelan nu angangan a kasaupuan kaliwsasakan a kitizaan. nauyaanay patizeng i Ke-s-mu nu satimulan, nika kilul tu kalamkam kacakat nu tukay atu capiay a kitizaan masatukuyay pahikukian mala u angangan tu nu iciba. baluhay kanatal a pihikukian imahini i En-tu-man a nipatizengan. a mikutay ciniza tu nu ayzaay a Ke-s-mu kanatal a pahikukian mala nu Su-tan nu satabakiay a pahikukian. . malalitin tu i hekalay atu zumaay a natinengan

== kakiliman == Ke-s-mo "A-la-pow a kamo الخرطوم‎ al-Kharṭūm, kamo nipabelin Ke-s-mo" no So-tan kong-hee-kow a angangan. makayzaay U-kan-taay a Ni-low-he ato makayzaan I-so-pi-yaay a Cin-ni-low-he itini a makakotay, pasayamis belod pasay Ay-ci ato molaliw micomod to Ti-cong-hey. "Ke-s-mo" cacay ko kamo o imi zo a cihek. Ke-s-mo a kitizaan iza ko100 emang ko moenengay no tademaw, micapi to saamisan no Ke-s-mo ato En-to-man a nisakapot no tabakiay a tokay o tademaw hakay macaliway to 400 a emang. likisi 歷史 Ke-s-mo i 1821 a mihcaan o Ay-ci ato Mo-han-mo-te.A-li-pow-sya patizeng to tokay, mala no Ay-ci a hitay a katokohan. nika zikoz balaki paso tobang patahkal kitizaan sapisiwbayno angangan. 1884 a mihca 3 a bolad 13 a dimiad, paicelang to Mo-han-mo-te.Ay-ha-man-te.Ma-he-ti sakapot a hitay mitaliyok to no Ing-kow sakakaay no mikeliday ci Ca-li.cyaw-ce.ke-ten mikelid mipopo to hitay, zikoz sakay tiniay a tokay no Ing-Ay polong no hitay sebek amipatay. 1885 a mihca 1 a bolad 26 a ddimiad, mapelpelay a Ke-s-mo mangayaw. zikoz I 1898 a mihca 9 a bolad 2 adimiad, ci He-pow-te.Ci-ci-le mikelid to Ing a hitay mademe t oko misebengay no Ma-he-ti-pay a hitay. 1885年1月26日, . 1899 a mihcaan, Ke-s-mo mala no Ing-Ay-So-tan angangan no tokay. i 1956 a mihcaan sateked mala no So-tan zikoz mala oyni angangan no kanatal. 1899年, . hekal地理 Ke-s-mo tini i So-tanno macelcelay no tademaw a kakitizaan no teban, mahamin itini a kanatal no Walian saamisan angangan, pey-wi15 katokoh 16 to, tong-cin 31 katokoh 32 to. Ke-s-mo a dimiad o akoti'ay a alikelikenan, pito a bolad ato walo a bolad taneng mahapinang maazih ko kasinanom. Ke-s-mo palalecad paymihcaan kasinanom macaliway ko 155 haw-mi. tini I mihcaan palalecad to bali no akoti', Ke-s-mo o sataledesay no tabakiay a tokay. kalalodan akoti' hakay a macaliway ko 53˚C "127˚F". mihcaan palalecad satalakaway akoti' no lahod 37.1˚C "99˚F". namahiza nayay ko cacanan palalecad to no boladay a akoti' isasa to 30˚C "86˚F". oyni caay henay kaazih zomaay angangan akoti' ko likelikenan demiad no tokay Li-ya-te, Pa-ke-ta-ato Bong-hwang a tokay mahiniay. o akoti' i labii mahapinang maselep ko akoti', Ke-s-mo palalecad saisasaay a lahod a didi' ko akoti'. Ke-s-mo iza ko So-tan satabakiay a pahikokia. no So-tanay a pibahelan no angangan a kasaopoan kaliwsasakan a kitizaan. naoyaanay patizeng i Ke-s-mo no satimolan, nika kilol to kalamkam kacakat no tokay ato capiay a kitizaan masatokoyay pahikokian mala o angangan to no iciba. balohay kanatal a pihikokian imahini i En-to-man a nipatizengan. a mikotay ciniza to no ayzaay a Ke-s-mo kanatal a pahikokian mala no So-tan no satabakiay a pahikokian. . malalitin to i hekalay ato zomaay a natinengan
